988574/</guid></item><item><title>科德角海岸附近的海盗沉船事件刷新了西非黄金的历史记录</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/pirate-shipwreck-off-the-coast-of-cape-cod-sets-the-historical-record-straight-on-west-african-gold-180988572/</link><description>欧洲人散布有关阿坎贸易伙伴黄金品质下降的谣言。对“Whydah Gally”沉船文物的新分析讲述了一个不同的故事</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 17:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/pirate-shipwreck-off-the-coast-of-cape-cod-sets-the-historical-record-straight-on-west-african-gold-180988572/</guid></item><item><title>最新研究表明，这些聪明的祖先可能和现代人类一样喜爱水晶</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/newly-discovered-stone-tools-made-from-geodes-and-fossils-hint-at-homo-erectus-connection-with-the-cosmos-180988565/</link><description>以色列考古学家出土了直立人用化石和水晶等石头制成的史前手斧，这也许是他们想要与宇宙联系的标志</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/newly-discovered-stone-tools-made-from-geodes-and-fossils-hint-at-homo-erectus-connection-with-the-cosmos-180988565/</guid></item><item><title>这座中世纪城堡坐落在史前时间胶囊的顶部。新的发掘可能揭示英国尼安德特人的历史</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-medieval-castle-sits-atop-a-prehistoric-time-capsule-new-excavations-could-reveal-the-history-of-neanderthals-in-britain-180988562/</link><description>在威尔士地标下方的一个洞穴中，考古学家发现了过去 12 万年来人类和动物来访的证据。现在，他们正在启动为期五年的挖掘项目</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-medieval-castle-sits-atop-a-prehistoric-time-capsule-new-excavations-could-reveal-the-history-of-neanderthals-in-britain-180988562/</guid></item><item><title>1996 年，辣妹组合永远改变了流行音乐。三十年后，她们的标志性服装在伦敦举办的新展览中展出</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/spice-girls-changed-pop-forever-in-1996-thirty-years-later-their-iconic-outfits-are-on-display-in-a-new-exhibition-in-london-180988569/</link><description>巴比肯音乐图书馆正在通过一场演出来庆祝英国流行文化，其中包括 Mel B 的豹纹紧身衣、Emma Bunton 的蓝色连衣裙和 Geri Halliwell 的英国国旗靴子</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/spice-girls-changed-pop-forever-in-1996-thirty-years-later-their-iconic-outfits-are-on-display-in-a-new-exhibition-in-london-180988569/</guid></item><item><title>在困难时期，玛雅人拒绝了神圣的王权。这座新发现的公共建筑揭示了向共享电力的过渡是如何展开的</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-times-trouble-maya-rejected-divine-kingship-newly-discovered-public-building-reveals-how-the-transition-to-shared-power-unfolded-180988567/</link><description>危地马拉北部的考古学家发现了一个带柱廊的开放式大厅，可能曾用作议会大厦，当地领导人和普通民众在这里会面讨论政治问题</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-times-trouble-maya-rejected-divine-kingship-newly-discovered-public-building-reveals-how-the-transition-to-shared-power-unfolded-180988567/</guid></item><item><title>科学家仍然不知道大峡谷是如何或何时形成的。新研究可能暗示其古老起源</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-still-dont-know-how-or-when-the-grand-canyon-formed-new-research-may-hint-at-its-ancient-origins-180988570/</link><description>研究人员表示，大约 660 万年前，古老的科罗拉多河在亚利桑那州北部形成了一个古老的湖泊，该湖泊向西溢出，最终形成了大峡谷</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 19:11:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-still-dont-know-how-or-when-the-grand-canyon-formed-new-research-may-hint-at-its-ancient-origins-180988570/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦莎士比亚故居已消失在历史之中。一位学者在档案中发现了一张地图，显示了其确切位置</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shakespeares-house-in-london-was-lost-to-history-a-scholar-discovered-a-map-in-the-archives-that-revealed-its-exact-location-180988566/</link><description>这位诗人在 1616 年去世前三年购买了这处房产。他是否希望在这座他创作最著名戏剧的城市度过更多时光？</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 18:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shakespeares-house-in-london-was-lost-to-history-a-scholar-discovered-a-map-in-the-archives-that-revealed-its-exact-location-180988566/</guid></item></channel></rss>